        <profileDesc>
            <creation when="1548"> it was written at <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC6847Agraro">ʾAgrāro</placeName>, which was then the royal seat of King 
                <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4428Galawdew">Galāwdewos</persName>.
            </creation>
            <langUsage><language ident="gez">Gǝʿǝz</language></langUsage>
            <abstract>
                <p>
                    It is a royal edict banning the trafficking of Christians and their sale to Arab owners
                    under the penalty of death.
                </p>
            </abstract>
